front.title: •Innocent Scoundrel
front.gametext: USED: If your gambler was just targeted by a weapon, opponent must choose to select a new target or lose 2 Force.  LOST: Cancel any Effect (except those immune to Alter) deployed on Han or your Lando.
front.lore: 'Well, that was a long time ago. I'm sure he's forgotten about that.' Since he needed Calrissian's help, Han regretted having introduced Lando to the Tonnika sisters.

cancels: An Effect deployed on Han or Lando
